This is not a wrapper on the original gridster jQuery plugin (http://gridster.net/). It is instead completely rewritten as Angular directives. Rewriting allowed for some additional features and better use of Angular data binding. Even more importantly, the original plugin had unpredictable behavior and crashed when wrapped with an Angular directive in my initial tests.
DISCLAIMER: This package is created by Ronald Zarīts, not the author of the library. This is simply a repackaging for use by NuGet Users, who, for one reason or another, still can't use Bower to manage client side dependencies.
